<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause id="_a4986039-4136-4799-b806-39b70fa9fed6" outputclass="ncc-clause"><meta><facet building="Class 2"/><facet building="Class 3"/><facet building="Class 4"/><facet building="Class 5"/><facet building="Class 6"/><facet building="Class 7a"/><facet building="Class 7b"/><facet building="Class 8"/><facet building="Class 9a"/><facet building="Class 9b"/><facet building="Class 9c"/></meta><sptc>H3O1</sptc><title id="_6af2c483-5ea5-48ac-8d80-4f8d6ba49de7">Objective</title><archive-num>2019: O2.3</archive-num><subclause id="_38d8391f-5ac8-4408-bf7f-58615fa80b2e" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_b64c3e23-10f6-4aab-b004-6c82980024d8">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>The Objective is to—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_fcfe2d2e-eabd-42a6-bffe-989bb4f49c6f">safeguard the occupants from illness or injury by alerting them of a fire in the building so that they may safely evacuate; and</li><li id="_d44c272f-087f-4b42-9af4-920cbee2e79b">avoid the spread of fire.</li></ol></subclause></clause>